Grammar

Rule 0     S' -> statements
Rule 1     statements -> statements statement
Rule 2     statements -> statement
Rule 3     statement -> RULE ID EQUALS expression
Rule 4     expression -> expression AND condition
Rule 5     expression -> expression OR condition
Rule 6     expression -> condition
Rule 7     condition -> ID GT NUMBER
Rule 8     condition -> ID LT NUMBER
Rule 9     condition -> ID GTE NUMBER
Rule 10    condition -> ID LTE NUMBER

Terminals, with rules where they appear

AND                  : 4
EQUALS               : 3
GT                   : 7
GTE                  : 9
ID                   : 3 7 8 9 10
LT                   : 8
LTE                  : 10
NUMBER               : 7 8 9 10
OR                   : 5
RULE                 : 3
error                : 

Nonterminals, with rules where they appear

condition            : 4 5 6
expression           : 3 4 5
statement            : 1 2
statements           : 1 0

Parsing method: LALR

state 0

    (0) S' -> . statements
    (1) statements -> . statements statement
    (2) statements -> . statement
    (3) statement -> . RULE ID EQUALS expression

    RULE            shift and go to state 3

    statements                     shift and go to state 1
    statement                      shift and go to state 2

state 1

    (0) S' -> statements .
    (1) statements -> statements . statement
    (3) statement -> . RULE ID EQUALS expression

    RULE            shift and go to state 3

    statement                      shift and go to state 4

state 2

    (2) statements -> statement .

    RULE            reduce using rule 2 (statements -> statement .)
    $end            reduce using rule 2 (statements -> statement .)


state 3

    (3) statement -> RULE . ID EQUALS expression

    ID              shift and go to state 5


state 4

    (1) statements -> statements statement .

    RULE            reduce using rule 1 (statements -> statements statement .)
    $end            reduce using rule 1 (statements -> statements statement .)


state 5

    (3) statement -> RULE ID . EQUALS expression

    EQUALS          shift and go to state 6


state 6

    (3) statement -> RULE ID EQUALS . expression
    (4) expression -> . expression AND condition
    (5) expression -> . expression OR condition
    (6) expression -> . condition
    (7) condition -> . ID GT NUMBER
    (8) condition -> . ID LT NUMBER
    (9) condition -> . ID GTE NUMBER
    (10) condition -> . ID LTE NUMBER

    ID              shift and go to state 7

    expression                     shift and go to state 8
    condition                      shift and go to state 9

state 7

    (7) condition -> ID . GT NUMBER
    (8) condition -> ID . LT NUMBER
    (9) condition -> ID . GTE NUMBER
    (10) condition -> ID . LTE NUMBER

    GT              shift and go to state 10
    LT              shift and go to state 11
    GTE             shift and go to state 12
    LTE             shift and go to state 13


state 8

    (3) statement -> RULE ID EQUALS expression .
    (4) expression -> expression . AND condition
    (5) expression -> expression . OR condition

    RULE            reduce using rule 3 (statement -> RULE ID EQUALS expression .)
    $end            reduce using rule 3 (statement -> RULE ID EQUALS expression .)
    AND             shift and go to state 14
    OR              shift and go to state 15


state 9

    (6) expression -> condition .

    AND             reduce using rule 6 (expression -> condition .)
    OR              reduce using rule 6 (expression -> condition .)
    RULE            reduce using rule 6 (expression -> condition .)
    $end            reduce using rule 6 (expression -> condition .)


state 10

    (7) condition -> ID GT . NUMBER

    NUMBER          shift and go to state 16


state 11

    (8) condition -> ID LT . NUMBER

    NUMBER          shift and go to state 17


state 12

    (9) condition -> ID GTE . NUMBER

    NUMBER          shift and go to state 18


state 13

    (10) condition -> ID LTE . NUMBER

    NUMBER          shift and go to state 19


state 14

    (4) expression -> expression AND . condition
    (7) condition -> . ID GT NUMBER
    (8) condition -> . ID LT NUMBER
    (9) condition -> . ID GTE NUMBER
    (10) condition -> . ID LTE NUMBER

    ID              shift and go to state 7

    condition                      shift and go to state 20

state 15

    (5) expression -> expression OR . condition
    (7) condition -> . ID GT NUMBER
    (8) condition -> . ID LT NUMBER
    (9) condition -> . ID GTE NUMBER
    (10) condition -> . ID LTE NUMBER

    ID              shift and go to state 7

    condition                      shift and go to state 21

state 16

    (7) condition -> ID GT NUMBER .

    AND             reduce using rule 7 (condition -> ID GT NUMBER .)
    OR              reduce using rule 7 (condition -> ID GT NUMBER .)
    RULE            reduce using rule 7 (condition -> ID GT NUMBER .)
    $end            reduce using rule 7 (condition -> ID GT NUMBER .)


state 17

    (8) condition -> ID LT NUMBER .

    AND             reduce using rule 8 (condition -> ID LT NUMBER .)
    OR              reduce using rule 8 (condition -> ID LT NUMBER .)
    RULE            reduce using rule 8 (condition -> ID LT NUMBER .)
    $end            reduce using rule 8 (condition -> ID LT NUMBER .)


state 18

    (9) condition -> ID GTE NUMBER .

    AND             reduce using rule 9 (condition -> ID GTE NUMBER .)
    OR              reduce using rule 9 (condition -> ID GTE NUMBER .)
    RULE            reduce using rule 9 (condition -> ID GTE NUMBER .)
    $end            reduce using rule 9 (condition -> ID GTE NUMBER .)


state 19

    (10) condition -> ID LTE NUMBER .

    AND             reduce using rule 10 (condition -> ID LTE NUMBER .)
    OR              reduce using rule 10 (condition -> ID LTE NUMBER .)
    RULE            reduce using rule 10 (condition -> ID LTE NUMBER .)
    $end            reduce using rule 10 (condition -> ID LTE NUMBER .)


state 20

    (4) expression -> expression AND condition .

    AND             reduce using rule 4 (expression -> expression AND condition .)
    OR              reduce using rule 4 (expression -> expression AND condition .)
    RULE            reduce using rule 4 (expression -> expression AND condition .)
    $end            reduce using rule 4 (expression -> expression AND condition .)


state 21

    (5) expression -> expression OR condition .

    AND             reduce using rule 5 (expression -> expression OR condition .)
    OR              reduce using rule 5 (expression -> expression OR condition .)
    RULE            reduce using rule 5 (expression -> expression OR condition .)
    $end            reduce using rule 5 (expression -> expression OR condition .)

